<DIV class=3Dabstract>
<H2 class=3Dnarrow><A id=3Dabstract shape=3Drect =
name=3Dabstract>Abstract</A></H2>
<P>This document describes requirements for general Japanese layout =
realized=20
with technologies like CSS, SVG and XSL-FO. The document is mainly based =
on a=20
standard for Japanese layout, JIS X 4051. However, it addresses also =
areas which=20
are not covered by JIS X 4051. The document is currently in draft stage. =

</P></DIV>
